<span class="line"><span style="color:#A6ACCD;">/dev/sda2 \xA0 \xA0 \xA0 \xA0 2099200 \xA0 \xA033554431 \xA0 \xA015727616 \xA0 8e \xA0Linux LVM</span></span>
